  .modal-body
    %h3 Formatting Guide
    %ul
      %li
        <h3>Headings</h3>
        %ul
          %li Headings are created by putting pounds signs before the text.
          %li The fewer the pound signs the larger the text
          %li= "# Title ->"
          <h1>Title</h1>
          %li= "### Title ->"
          <h3>Title</h3>
      %li
        <h3>Lists</h3>
        %ul
          %li You can create either bulleted or numbered lists
          %li Bulleted lists are created by putting a * before list item
          %li Numbered lists are created by putting a number followed by a period before the item
          %li
            * 1 cup of water
            <br>
            * 1 glass
          %li
            1. Put water in glass
            <br>
            2. Drink water
      %li
        <h3>Images</h3>
        %ul
          %li The suggested way to post images here is to upload them to a site like
          %a{:href => "http://www.imgur.com"}= "Imgur"
          %li
            They can then be displayed using this syntax ![image_name](image_link)
